ActPlant Protection Act
PrecisEnactment of the PHYTOPHTHORA RAMORUM COMPENSATION REGULATIONS which provide for the payment of compensation to nursery owners and others affected by efforts to eradicate Phytophthora ramorum, a fungus causing Sudden Oak Death which has infected areas in British Columbia.
